        <p>
          Logging as a CSV events looks like this:
        </p>
        <pre class="prettyprint linenums">
logger.debug("one={}, two={}, three={}", 1, 2, 3);
</pre>
        <p>
          Produces a CSV record with the following fields:
          <ol>
            <li>Time Nanos</li>
            <li>Time Millis</li>
            <li>Level</li>
            <li>Thread ID</li>
            <li>Thread Name</li>
            <li>Thread Priority</li>
            <li>Formatted Message</li>
            <li>Logger FQCN</li>
            <li>Logger Name</li>
            <li>Marker</li>
            <li>Thrown Proxy</li>
            <li>Source</li>
            <li>Context Map</li>
            <li>Context Stack</li>
          </ol>
        </p>
