                <p>Generating <a href="#LocationInformation">location information</a>
                is an expensive operation and may impact performance. Use with caution.</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>title</td>
              <td>String</td>
              <td>A String that will appear as the HTML title.</td>
            </tr>
